[normal]&#xa0;[bold]How should complaints about the Parliamentary and Health Service Ombudsman be handled?[bold]Answer[bold]: B[bold]y an Independ[bold]ent Assessor, as an [bold]appeal [bold]body [bold]when a clearly laid-out[bold] internal complaints procedure has not given satisfaction.[bold]This sh
