[normal]&#xa0;[bold]How effectiv[bold]ely does the Parliamentary and H[bold]ealth Service Ombudsman deal with [bold]complaints?[bold]Answer[bold]:[bold] On[bold] the basis of my experience[bold], [bold]unconvincingly. [bold]I did get some acknowledgments of 
[normal]procedural 
